---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Company — KYDE"
  description="KYDE is building the trust infrastructure for the agentic economy. The governance layer that gives AI agents real economic authority while keeping humans in control."
>
  <Navbar />

  <main>

    <!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-36 pb-24 md:pt-48 md:pb-36">
      <div class="bg-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute top-0 left-0 h-[600px] w-[800px] rounded-full bg-violet-600/5 blur-3xl"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-violet-400">Company</p>
        <h1 class="max-w-3xl text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
          The economy is going agentic.
          The infrastructure for trust doesn't exist yet.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-violet-400">We're building it.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ THE SHIFT ══════════ -->
    <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-zinc-900/30 to-black pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]">

          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-violet-400">The Shift</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Something fundamental is changing.</p>
            <p>
              For decades, software executed instructions. Humans decided. Humans acted. The software was a tool — precise, obedient, inert.
            </p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-base border-l-2 border-zinc-700 pl-5">
              That model is ending.
            </p>
            <p>
              AI agents don't wait for instructions. They reason, plan, and act. They book meetings, execute transactions, write and deploy code, manage customer relationships, and make procurement decisions — autonomously, at scale, faster than any human can supervise.
            </p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-white">
              This is not a future scenario. It is happening now. In your organization. Across every industry.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ THE PROBLEM ══════════ -->
    <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]">

          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-violet-400">The Problem With Speed</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
            <p>
              The agentic shift is creating economic value at a pace we haven't seen since the internet. But it is also creating a governance vacuum.
            </p>
            <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="rounded-sm border border-emerald-400/20 bg-zinc-900/60 p-6">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">When a human takes a business decision</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">There is a legal framework — contracts, liability, corporate law, audit trails. The accountability structure is centuries old. It is imperfect, but it exists.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-sm border border-red-400/20 bg-zinc-900/60 p-6">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">When an AI agent takes a business decision</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">There is almost nothing. The agent acts. Something happens. A log entry may or may not exist. Whether it can be trusted, verified, or produced in a regulatory inquiry is an open question for most organizations.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>
              Regulators have noticed. The EU AI Act, NIS-2, DORA, and GDPR are not the end of the compliance wave. They are the beginning.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ WHAT WE'RE BUILDING ══════════ -->
    <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-zinc-900/30 to-black pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]">

          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-violet-400">What KYDE Is Building</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">
              KYDE is building the trust infrastructure for the agentic economy.
            </p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">Not a filter. Not a firewall. Not another observability dashboard.</p>
            <p>
              Governance infrastructure — the layer that gives AI agents real economic authority while keeping humans in control of the boundaries.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4 border-l-2 border-violet-500/30 pl-6">
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Near term</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mt-1">A tamper-evident append-only database for every AI agent action. Evidence that cannot be altered. Records that regulators, auditors, and courts can trust.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Longer term</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mt-1">Machine-readable policies that travel with every agent. Cryptographically signed mandates. A delegation model that lets organizations give AI agents genuine authority — with verifiable, unbreakable limits.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-sm border border-violet-500/20 bg-violet-600/5 px-8 py-6">
              <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-200">
                Think of what corporate law did for the limited liability company — it created a legal structure that enabled economic actors to operate with defined rights, responsibilities, and accountability.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">
                KYDE is building that structure for non-human economic actors.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ WHY NOW ══════════ -->
    <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]">

          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-violet-400">Why Now</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="text-lg text-zinc-300 mb-10">Three forces are converging.</p>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              {[
                {
                  n: '01',
                  title: 'Regulatory enforcement is real.',
                  body: 'EU AI Act High-Risk enforcement begins August 2, 2026. NIS-2 is already in force. DORA is in force. The compliance deadlines are not hypothetical.',
                  color: 'amber',
                },
                {
                  n: '02',
                  title: 'Agent deployment is accelerating.',
                  body: 'Every major enterprise is running AI agents today — often without knowing exactly what those agents are doing, why, or whether the record of their actions can be trusted.',
                  color: 'violet',
                },
                {
                  n: '03',
                  title: 'The window to define the infrastructure layer is open.',
                  body: 'Trust infrastructure, like all infrastructure, is built once and depended on for decades. The organization that defines the governance standard for AI agents becomes the foundation everything else is built on.',
                  color: 'cyan',
                },
              ].map(({ n, title, body, color }) => (
                <div class={`flex gap-6 rounded-sm border bg-zinc-900/40 p-8 ${
                  color === 'amber' ? 'border-amber-400/20' :
                  color === 'violet' ? 'border-violet-400/20' :
                  'border-cyan-400/20'
                }`}>
                  <span class={`font-mono text-3xl font-bold shrink-0 ${
                    color === 'amber' ? 'text-amber-400/40' :
                    color === 'violet' ? 'text-violet-400/40' :
                    'text-cyan-400/40'
                  }`}>{n}</span>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2">{title}</p>
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">{body}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ CTA ══════════ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="rounded-sm border border-violet-500/20 bg-violet-600/5 p-12 md:p-16">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
              Want to learn more or get involved?
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-300">
              We're early. If you're building in regulated industries, we want to talk.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <button
                onclick="openModal()"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-sm bg-violet-600 px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-violet-600/25 hover:bg-violet-500 transition-all"
              >
                Book a Demo →
              </button>
              <a
                href="mailto:hello@kyde.com"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-sm border border-zinc-700 px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 hover:border-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-all"
              >
                hello@kyde.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>
